\bf{The\ no.\; of\; equivalence\; relation\; on\;  n-\; set\; is \; equal\; to \ no.\; of \; partition \; of \; n-set  }
\{a,b,c\}
\{a|b|c\}\;,\{a|b,c\}\;,\{b|c,a\}\;,\{c|a,b\}\;,\{a,b,c\}
